<bibRefCitation id="5D2C4B1AD051FFECC18AF926FE946113" author="Kantvilas, G." box="[136,328,1776,1802]" pageId="3" pageNumber="212" pagination="349 - 364" refId="ref7624" refString="Kantvilas, G. (2014) New species of the genus Rimularia Nyl. from Tasmania. Lichenologist 46: 349 - 364. https: // doi. org / 10.1017 / S 0024282913000595" type="journal article" year="2014">Kantvilas (2014)</bibRefCitation>
